@startuml
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam diagramBorderColor transparent
skinparam diagramBorderThickness 0

skinparam participant {
  BorderColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #eeeeee
  FontSize 13
  FontColor #333333
  Padding 8
}

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  ArrowThickness 1.5
  LifeLineBorderColor #bbbbbb
  ArrowFontSize 11
  ArrowFontColor #444444
}

skinparam noteFontSize 11



participant "주문" as O
participant "상품" as P
participant "배달" as D

O -> P: ① 재고 감소 요청
P --> O: ② 성공
note left: productDecreased = true

O -> D: ③ 배달 생성 요청
D -[#cc0000]-> O: ④ 실패

note over O: catch → productDecreased 확인

O -[#cc0000]> P: ⑤ 재고 복구 요청 (보상)
P --> O: ⑥ 성공

note over O: Exception500 반환\n(데이터 일관성 유지)

@enduml
